<h2>Installation</h2>
<ol>
<li><b>download the zip file (either full or the platform specific version)</b></li>
<li><b>unzip</b></li>
<li><b>edit pl_manager.conf to reflect your info</b></li>
<li><b>execute run_%your platform%.sh</b></li>
<li>(If the controller is running already, but you want to attach a new instance of the gui, execute run_%your platform%_gui.sh)</li>
</ol>


